2 kids, PCOS, working mom. I prioritize myself. I focus on creating healthy habits. Movement, healthy diet, nothing too dramatic. I'm too close to an overweight BMI, it messes with my mind. But I can't go back, can't give up. I'll continue working on the inside until I feel better on the outside.

My biggest solo accomplishment has been a half marathon. Getting ready for a full, but have to mix in moving, building a house, kid starting kindergarten, and marriage. One day.</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/hTML0Rd</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[Monkeysboobsbutts]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>uh</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/tI58Q4U</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/QWEIb2T.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/tI58Q4U</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[AsshatTheCat]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Streets Ahead - Britta Perry Cosplay</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/EaDfA28</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/xC5MIe2.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>I know what it is. It's like a thought... with another thoughts hat on.</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/EaDfA28</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[Alsoashley]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>The Amazing Awoo Duo</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/iHLPKAU</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/tBkut2E.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/iHLPKAU</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[michaelv2]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>-</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/tTX4Rvn</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/k9p1AFy.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/tTX4Rvn</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[mfrybeasley]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>True</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/20KNjLJ</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/Q8JjaQ2.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></descrip